name: Deepverse
description: Ad Hoc Orquestra is a project based on collective improvisation, creating music in real time and promoting the encounter between multiple artists. Deepverse was improvised and recorded live with the collaboration of Chris Martins,Paulo Prot, Maycon Lack, Ricardo Passos, Victor Mendes, Bernardo Bauer, PC Guimarães, Antônio Silva, Antônio Beirão, Lucas Ferrari, Daniel Tamietti. Conducted by Guilherme Peluci. Belo Horizonte, Brazil, 2018. Artwork by AdHoc.
